        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Basement Window Replacement</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">General basement window replacement for older Seward properties where the frame or glass has failed, even outside of a formal egress upgrade.</p>
      </div>
</div>
